metadata.name: ButtFacesNFT #1
metadata.description: It is year 4000 and humans have evolved to face the increasing harshness of the world as it is made unrecognizable through climate change. The unstable atmosphere of earth now allows an unprecedented amount of gamma rays to reach the surface, causing rapid mutations in all biological life forms. Most surviving humans have evolved with their critical organs shielded by pants, and now have faces on their butts. This new step in evolution brings us to a place where humanity must work together to survive. We are many butts, many faces, butt one community. https://www.buttfaces.xyz
